<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200330/9f9f60d93a854be989f5b1fb34045290.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200330/498c74217b6547deb3545d7c84f757f1.png" max-width="600" /></p>